<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Dunno if this will help, but when we got him yesterday we had a couple snaffu's before getting ready and the ranger had to track this guy for about 30 minutes before we killed him (totem 8). He seems to make a figure eight that crosses the center island. If he is always on the same path, he hits shore from the goblin camp to unrest zone, crosses the island, follows the shore on the other side east of the BB zone for a bit, then comes back across the island. If he follows standard verant spawn rules (no reason why he shouldn't) I would expect his placeholder follows about the same pattern. In other words, nuke everything that humps over the island and bring something soft to sit on.</font></td></tr></table>
