<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Twinked</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-03 06:52:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have the Kedge totem (on the Bristlebain server). I lucked out, and got it on the FIRST Bilge kill I ever did. One point, Bilge casts Greater Heal like mad on himself. I have seen Bilge kill a 40th level warrior by himself, because the warrior couldn't keep up with his healing, even with 2 Ykeshas. Usually he doesn't heal that much, but if he does, run like hell. (I just blew him up with my wizard, and it still took 7 conflagurations at 625 a hit to outnuke his dang healing rate).</font></td></tr></table>
