<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Bilge is one of two annoying water goblins that clerics have to hunt to get a piece for their clerical-type armor.  Bilge drops I believe the Ingot of the Constant.  So if you see it on him, don't loot unless you'rea cleric.  If there's no clerics in your group, do a shout or call a cleric friend.  We appreciate it greatly when people do that.  :)</font></td></tr></table>
